OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with some
OL,6,Fbrightness in the east. Then rain will
OL,7,Fspread southeast across all parts from
OL,8,Flate morning. Drier weather with a few
OL,9,Fshowers will follow on by late
OL,10,Fafternoon. Mild this morning, but
OL,11,Fturning colder this afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA few showers this evening.
OL,14,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,15,Fmainly dry with clear periods and just
OL,16,Fthe odd shower. Cold with patchy frost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FMost of the day will be dry,
OL,19,Fsome early brightness. Outbreaks of
OL,20,Frain spreading east towards evening.
OL,21,FColder than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
